Restaurant
- Students would be able to view the available items from the restaurant for ordering
- Students would be able to select which items and how many of each to order
- Students would be able to review their order before checkout
- Students would be able to view the receipt and status of their order

- Admin would be able to view the list of orders and the items they ordered
- Admin would be able to approve the orders
- Admin would be able to update the order status
- Once the order has been accepted, the stock of that product would be deducted